            "title": "AI Workspace Hub",
            "summary": "A focused workspace interface for managing AI tasks, projects, and collaborative workflows. Clean, minimal design with warm neutrals and intuitive navigation.",
            "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  <title>AI Workspace</title>\n  <style>\n    :root {\n      --bg: #FFF8F0;\n      --card: #FFF;\n      --accent: #FF8C69;\n      --text: #4A3E38;\n      --muted: #A1887F;\n      --radius: 16px;\n      --space: 20px;\n    }\n    * {\n      margin: 0;\n      padding: 0;\n      box-sizing: border-box;\n    }\n    body {\n      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;\n      background: var(--bg);\n      color: var(--text);\n      font-size: 16px;\n      line-height: 1.5;\n    }\n    .container {\n      width: 100%;\n      max-width: 375px;\n      margin: 0 auto;\n      padding: var(--space);\n      min-height: 100vh;\n      display: flex;\n      flex-direction: column;\n      gap: var(--space);\n    }\n    .header {\n      display: flex;\n      justify-content: space-between;\n      align-items: center;\n      padding-bottom: var(--space);\n      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(74, 62, 56, 0.1);\n    }\n    .header h1 {\n      font-size: 28px;\n      font-weight: 600;\n    }\n    .header-action {\n      width: 40px;\n      height: 40px;\n      border-radius: 50%;\n      background: var(--card);\n      border: 1px solid rgba(74, 62, 56, 0.15);\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      justify-content: center;\n      font-size: 14px;\n      cursor: pointer;\n      color: var(--muted);\n    }\n    .section {\n      display: flex;\n      flex-direction: column;\n      gap: 12px;\n    }\n    .section-title {\n      font-size: 14px;\n      font-weight: 600;\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      letter-spacing: 0.5px;\n      color: var(--muted);\n    }\n    .card {\n      background: var(--card);\n      border-radius: var(--radius);\n      padding: var(--space);\n      border: 1px solid rgba(74, 62, 56, 0.08);\n      display: flex;\n      flex-direction: column;\n      gap: 8px;\n    }\n    .card-title {\n      font-size: 16px;\n      font-weight: 600;\n      color: var(--text);\n    }\n    .card-desc {\n      font-size: 14px;\n      color: var(--muted);\n    }\n    .card-meta {\n      font-size: 12px;\n      color: rgba(74, 62, 56, 0.5);\n      margin-top: 4px;\n    }\n    .quick-actions {\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n      gap: 12px;\n    }\n    .action-btn {\n      background: var(--card);\n      border: 2px solid var(--accent);\n      border-radius: var(--radius);\n      padding: 16px 12px;\n      text-align: center;\n      font-size: 14px;\n      font-weight: 600;\n      color: var(--accent);\n      cursor: pointer;\n      transition: all 0.2s;\n    }\n    .action-btn:active {\n      background: rgba(255, 140, 105, 0.1);\n    }\n    .primary-btn {\n      background: var(--accent);\n      color: #FFF;\n      border: none;\n      padding: 16px;\n      border-radius: var(--radius);\n      font-size: 16px;\n      font-weight: 600;\n      cursor: pointer;\n      width: 100%;\n      transition: all 0.2s;\n    }\n    .primary-btn:active {\n      opacity: 0.9;\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <div class=\"header\">\n      <h1>Workspace</h1>\n      <div class=\"header-action\">⚙</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"section\">\n      <div class=\"section-title\">Active Projects</div>\n      <div class=\"card\">\n        <div class=\"card-title\">Content Strategy Q1</div>\n        <div class=\"card-desc\">Outline and research phase</div>\n        <div class=\"card-meta\">3 tasks • Due Jan 28</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"card\">\n        <div class=\"card-title\">Product Documentation</div>\n        <div class=\"card-desc\">API reference and guides</div>\n        <div class=\"card-meta\">5 tasks • Due Feb 5</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"section\">\n      <div class=\"section-title\">Quick Actions</div>\n      <div class=\"quick-actions\">\n        <button class=\"action-btn\">New Task</button>\n        <button class=\"action-btn\">New Project</button>\n        <button class=\"action-btn\">Templates</button>\n        <button class=\"action-btn\">Collaborate</button>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"section\" style=\"margin-top: auto;\">\n      <button class=\"primary-btn\">Start New Session</button>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</body>\n</html>",
